*ufw-0.33-r2 (06 Dec 2012)
*ufw-0.31.1-r2 (06 Dec 2012)

  06 Dec 2012; Ian Whyman <thev00d00@gentoo.org> -ufw-0.31.1-r1.ebuild,
  +ufw-0.31.1-r2.ebuild, -ufw-0.33-r1.ebuild, +ufw-0.33-r2.ebuild:
